cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.HC 

This paper involves the use of deep learning networks to forecast future visual fields, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of artificial neural networks also falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the study involves the analysis of medical data, which falls under human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
